data.description:
WOW New Amazing Price!!!
 This charming 4 bedroom, 2 bath home in the desirable Moore School district is ready for its new owner! Featuring a large kitchen with tons of storage, granite countertops, center island, stainless steel appliances, and the refrigerator is included! Beautiful formal dining room, second dining area in the kitchen, 4th bedroom can be an office, and the Two large living areas would be great for entertaining. In the living area you will find a lovely floor to ceiling brick gas burning fireplace with mental, crown molding, and large windows that bring in lots of natural sunlight. The grand master suite boasts vaulted ceilings, new carpet, new ceiling fan, and a window seat. The en-suite offers a relaxing jetted tub, double vanities, and a walk-in shower. Three car driveway with access to the backyard, storm shelter the garage and two new garage doors. Walking distance of Eastlake Elementary and Westmoore High School, close to shopping, and easy highway access. Don't miss out on this home, schedule you're private showing today!
